item.title: About
item.description: My name is Sansar. I live in Mongolia and work in banking industry with main focus on risk management function. I studied Mathematics at TU Darmstadt in Germany and have a passion for the endurance sports (swimming, cycling and data science ;-)). I am 2x Finisher of IRONMAN GERMANY 70.3 in Wiesbaden of Germany.
